    "Our evaluation indicates that Wazuh is the best solution in terms of security features and performance.",
    "Wazuh provides plenty of features and should be the first choice for organizations looking for a customizable SIEM solution.",
    "Although open-source SIEM solutions provide a powerful set of features that fit the requirements of most SMEs, they are not on par with their commercial counterparts.",
    "To improve the open-source SIEM solutions, we are currently working on some of the potential research directions.",
    "The first is the integration of unstructured Open Source Intelligence (OSINT) data by using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques."
